Title:
			公告ID：KYSA-202409-1077
公告摘要：linux-firmware安全漏洞
等级：重要
发布日期：2024-09-17
		
1.修复的漏洞
·CVE-2023-31315
描述：在特定模型寄存器（MSR）中存在不当验证，可能允许具有 ring0 访问权限的恶意程序在 SMI 锁定启用时修改 SMM 配置。这一问题可能导致任意代码执行。

2.受影响的软件包
·中标麒麟高级服务器操作系统 V7
·aarch64架构:
iwl2000-firmware、iwl6000-firmware、linux-firmware、iwl3160-firmware、iwl6000g2b-firmware、iwl2030-firmware、iwl4965-firmware、iwl5000-firmware、iwl5150-firmware、iwl6000g2a-firmware、iwl3945-firmware、iwl7260-firmware、iwl100-firmware、iwl105-firmware、iwl6050-firmware、iwl1000-firmware、iwl135-firmware
·x86_64架构:
iwl2000-firmware、iwl6000-firmware、linux-firmware、iwl3160-firmware、iwl6000g2b-firmware、iwl2030-firmware、iwl5000-firmware、iwl6000g2a-firmware、iwl7260-firmware、iwl5150-firmware、iwl3945-firmware、iwl4965-firmware、iwl100-firmware、iwl105-firmware、iwl6050-firmware、iwl1000-firmware、iwl135-firmware
·银河麒麟高级服务器操作系统 V10
·aarch64架构:
iwl2000-firmware、iwl6000-firmware、linux-firmware、iwl3160-firmware、iwl6000g2b-firmware、iwl2030-firmware、iwl5000-firmware、iwl6000g2a-firmware、iwl7260-firmware、iwl5150-firmware、iwl3945-firmware、iwl4965-firmware、iwl100-firmware、iwl105-firmware、iwl6050-firmware、iwl1000-firmware、iwl135-firmware
·x86_64架构:
iwl2000-firmware、iwl6000-firmware、linux-firmware、iwl3160-firmware、iwl6000g2b-firmware、iwl2030-firmware、iwl5000-firmware、iwl6000g2a-firmware、iwl5150-firmware、iwl7260-firmware、iwl3945-firmware、iwl4965-firmware、iwl100-firmware、iwl105-firmware、iwl6050-firmware、iwl1000-firmware、iwl135-firmware

